# PLAYER::SET_PLAYER_WANTED_LEVEL_NO_DROP

## Summary
Sets the wanted level only if its higher than the current

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player
* **INT** wantedLevel
* **BOOL** delayLawResponse = false

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
p2 is always false in R* scripts
